title: Ep. - 309 - MURDER ON MIDDLE BEACH CARMEL: WHO KILLED MARIA MARTA
description:
Kate reviews The Cult of The Family on Starz about Australia’s most notorious cult leader Anne Hamilton-Byrne.

 

Nick Rizzo, Senior Producer of Watch What Happens Live on Bravo helps Kate review HBO’s Murder on Middle Beach, about the unsolved murder of Barbara Hamburg.

 

Sarah and Danny from Not Another True Crime podcast help Kate review Netflix’s docuseries Carmel: Who Killed Maria Marta, about the unsolved murder of Maria Marta Garcia Belsunce.
